# Project Structure

This is project structure of this web application

## Main Structure
- We use Vite bundler with yarn to run the local server and building the product
- Main app is in `src/`
- React components are in `src/components/` folder
- Reusable react contexts are in `src/context/` folder
- Hooks are in `src/hooks/` folder
- Utils are in `src/utils/` folder
- We use React router dom for client side routing and its routes are in `src/routes/` folder
- API clients are in `src/api/` folder
- Translation files are in `src/i18n/` folder
  - Currently we support english, german translations
- Unit tests are part of same directory for component or utils, etc file
- Integration tests are in the `integration-tests/` folder


## Old codes
- We support two version of our product
- Old product uses material UI and styled components but we no loader develop anything for it. Its just in support mode. 
  - Code is in same folder and all files are mostly in PascelCase
- New product uses tailwind, radix colors, radix components
  - re-useable dumb UI compoents are in `src/components/shared/ui` folder.
  - we follow kabab case for folder and file names